{"tid":566987,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支那又送大禮]居支那來港男童染流感出現嚴重併發症","createTime":"2018-02-20T12:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T13:41:16.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fc2653b421b991dbb1626244e5fb7c05dab6b105","tid":566987,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T12:27:01.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心調查一宗兒童感染流感出現嚴重併發症個案。<br />\n<br />\n一名居於內地的7歲男童上星期四到港，星期日起出現發燒、咳嗽和肌肉疼痛等病徵，翌日出現身體抽搐，入住瑪麗醫院。他的鼻咽分泌樣本經化驗後，證實對甲型流感H1病毒呈陽性反應，臨床診斷為甲型流感併發腦病變，患者現時情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n中心表示，初步調查顯示病人沒有接種今季季節性流感疫苗，家居接觸者及同行人士至今沒有病徵，中心正繼續調查個案。<br />\n<br />\n中心又說，本地季節性流感活躍程度維持在高水平，加上學校農曆新年假期即將完結，已向學校發信，呼籲提高警覺及加強預防措施，減低季節性流感的影響。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1381714-20180220.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1381714-20180220.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2Fd4RTiGqAtN9HQfMtucQBxFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=e47c289b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1381714-20180220.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1c241df4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1381714-20180220.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"bb903151e61552cf6d80a896fd15630256812ac7","tid":566987,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T13:31:22.000Z","msg":"即刻拖去人道毀滅啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87be1dd7c7843ccab666ed87abc89ef4e03b2e6b","tid":566987,"uid":166663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T13:36:31.000Z","msg":"點解唔死翻大陸入院要留係香港醫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461febcb61bdc9191a4f415395df4ab83827f73f","tid":566987,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T13:41:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6746b65527f9eb4c0b6e8c427dc47ca996f2ba7","tid":566987,"uid":3617